efits, it is important to consume a complete amino acid profile  just as it is important to consume a variety of protein and carbohydrates for a healthy diet. Each amino acid plays a different role in your bodys metabolism and mechanics.','2015-10-01 04:46:09','2015-10-01 04:46:09'),
